{"tid":1945574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警三番四次洩露記者/議員及抗爭者資料俾藍絲暴徒群組 涉煽動憎恨","createTime":"2020-03-27T07:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T09:08:55.000Z","uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9950f46ce01956e8d7a2bc23d3d01ff515c8677b","tid":1945574,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T07:04:13.000Z","msg":"先有故意將立場記者身分證展露響鏡頭前達40秒<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好唔記得蘋果記者已經被襲擊</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n尋日葵涌警署又有黑警錄影民主黨議員<br />\n更甚係抹沒黑佢哋收錢示威<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>記住之前已經有好幾位議員包括岑子傑, 鄺俊宇被襲擊</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有無法無天死光頭警長<br />\n上微博咒罵香港醫護中武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\n講煽動仇恨 <br />\n你黑警皇軍最撚叻<br />\n你老母俾狗屌 <br />\n你老竇橫屍街頭<br />\n你中武漢肺炎做白警"},{"pid":"4340ce59d15efa5b8a41e438356bc61cf10fbaa7","tid":1945574,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T07:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204d2863829324a5082dedb30f1ff0465a24ad0c","tid":1945574,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23fff3d6684d9bfcad945a75920a424e7255f343","tid":1945574,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5af01ee0d5a9e26bf46f2119912d6d996fb5409","tid":1945574,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95c5eb65ea92b4a6d9183e7d650a2ec1b819c12","tid":1945574,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"652c59d9782fd06990a12091906ebc53accd67d2","tid":1945574,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-2